{"tid":831383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵揭幕很興奮】上京搭高鐵或飛機？ 鯨大代表：飛機時間短班次又多","createTime":"2018-09-22T02:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:43:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"12fa46e2438ff19dcc0e4fe897c6cceb48320950","tid":831383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段今早10時將在西九龍站舉行通車儀式，多名港區全國人大代表、政協、行會成員、建制派立法會議員和內地政府代表等，陸續抵達會場。<br />\n<br />\n本身為公開大學校長的港區全國人大代表黃玉山，在儀式開始前向傳媒表示，對高鐵香港段開通「很興奮」，形容開通具「劃時代意義」。<br />\n<br />\n黃玉山表示，從香港乘坐高鐵到北京需要8至9小時，而乘飛機有時候會延誤，兩者所需時間其實差不多，自己日後若有機會，都會試坐高鐵到北京。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有記者接着問黃玉山，乘飛機還是高鐵的機會較大，他又坦言「飛機較大機會」，因「時間短，班次又多」，但補充說自己對高鐵的認識「矇查查」，若日後方便，都可試坐高鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00001/1537577966978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00001%2F1537577966978&d=btRH%2BgKU%2F93JxdNHxl2m7J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=05d408a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00001%2F1537577966978&h=cf280498\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00001/1537577966978</a>"},{"pid":"73c830ca295056a6e37a8a11127410422796eabf","tid":831383,"uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"港共成班都精神病"},{"pid":"3801b1d1729894cdeb5e98d76b0ac6cc0f291e30","tid":831383,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e4d87d1f3b8f517ba2b53d1832c36d76bce2b2b","tid":831383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"高鐵有冇關愛座?"},{"pid":"7ce22ab3e4f98188aded528e09638d5e48c9f5d7","tid":831383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:57:02